<ul>
  <li>Understand the structure of a HTML5 page</li>
  <li>Learn how to access and manipulate CSS from the Chrome Developer Tools</li>
  <li>Layout semantic HTML using CSS</li>
  <li>Style HTML elements using CSS</li>
  <li>Apply CSS transformations and transitions</li>
</ul>

