<h2 id="full-group-instruction">Full-Group Instruction</h2>

<h3 id="anatomy-of-an-html-page">Anatomy of an HTML Page</h3>

<p>Clone the TuringBistro <a href="https://github.com/turingschool-examples/turing-bistro">repo</a>. As a group, weâ€™re going to go through the <code class="highlighter-rouge">index.html</code> in this repository and discuss the components. Feel free to interject and ask questions at this time.</p>

<h4 id="additional-discussion-points">Additional Discussion Points</h4>

<ul>
  <li>Chrome Developer Tools</li>
  <li><code class="highlighter-rouge">class</code> vs. <code class="highlighter-rouge">id</code></li>
  <li><a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/">Mozilla Developer Network</a></li>
</ul>

<h3 id="css-refresher">CSS Refresher</h3>

<p>As a group, weâ€™ll discuss the basics of CSS selectors and properties. Feel free to interject and ask questions.</p>

<h4 id="additional-discussion-points-1">Additional Discussion Points</h4>

<ul>
  <li><code class="highlighter-rouge">normalize.css</code></li>
